      "note_no": "143",
      "note": "According to Zamakhshari, the particle thumma at the beginning of this last clause does not signify a sequence in time (\"and then\" or \"afterwards\") but, rather, a stress on the impossibility (istib'ad) of their ever being succoured by God."
